      <title>冯德莱恩面临艰难的平衡之道，难以赢得欧盟第二任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/von-der-leyen-faces-tricky-balancing-act-to-seal-second-eu-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[理论上，在工党赢得欧盟选举多数席位后，乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩连任欧盟委员会主席应该会一帆风顺。但实际情况可能要复杂得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/von-der-leyen-faces-tricky-balancing-act-to-seal-second-eu-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 11:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟选举加剧政治风险 新兴货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继一系列备受瞩目的选举引发全球市场动荡之后，欧盟周末选举加剧了政治风险，导致全球大多数发展中经济体的货币走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/emerging-currencies-drop-as-eu-elections-add-to-political-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:51:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国未决选民拒绝苏纳克，保守党希望再遭打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/uk-s-undecided-voters-reject-sunak-in-latest-blow-to-tory-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民意调查分析显示，英国尚未决定的选民正在抛弃里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党，如果在 7 月 4 日的大选中再次出现这种情况，那么首相本已渺茫的执政机会将荡然无存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/uk-s-undecided-voters-reject-sunak-in-latest-blow-to-tory-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:43:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>绿色毁灭意味着欧洲为实现气候目标将面临艰巨斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/green-wipeout-means-fights-ahead-to-keep-europe-s-climate-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周末的欧盟选举标志着欧盟有史以来最绿色议会的结束，此前人们对从气候政策到移民等各方面的担忧给民粹主义者带来了推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/green-wipeout-means-fights-ahead-to-keep-europe-s-climate-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博民意调查发现，保守党未能削弱工党的领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-tories-fail-to-dent-labour-s-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，工党和保守党将公布各自的选举宣言，英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党需要拿出改变格局的举措，而彭博社的民意调查显示，迄今为止，在 19 天的竞选活动中，执政党未能对反对党造成影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-tories-fail-to-dent-labour-s-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
