      <title>莫迪选择内阁老面孔 等待财政部长上任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/modi-chooses-old-faces-in-cabinet-as-key-finance-post-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的新内阁将会有几位其前任政府的老面孔回归，但目前还不清楚他们将担任哪些职位，包括关键的财政部职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/modi-chooses-old-faces-in-cabinet-as-key-finance-post-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 05:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩妹妹警告称，垃圾气球飞越边境将遭到进一步报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/kim-s-sister-warns-of-further-reprisals-as-trash-balloons-fly-over-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人的妹妹警告称，韩国多年来首次恢复扩音器广播，标志着世界上军事化程度最高的边境之一的紧张局势升级，朝鲜将对韩国采取报复行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/kim-s-sister-warns-of-further-reprisals-as-trash-balloons-fly-over-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 00:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利新贵崛起，奥尔班的坚不可摧被打破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新晋政治家彼得·马扎尔 (Peter Magyar) 在欧洲议会选举中飙升至第二位，打破了匈牙利作为除了总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 的统治之外别无选择的国家的形象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</guid>
